#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Salma</firstname> <surname>Sultana</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>Salma</firstname> <surname>Sultana</surname>"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:664 tasks.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check Spelling"
msgstr "Õigekirja kontroll"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:666
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&sonnet; is the spelling checker used by &kde; applications such as "
#| "&kate;, &kmail;, and &kword;. It is a &GUI; frontend to various free "
#| "spell checkers."
msgid ""
"&sonnet; is the spelling checker used by &kde; applications such as &kate;, "
"&kmail;, and &calligrawords;. It is a &GUI; frontend to various free spell "
"checkers."
msgstr ""
"Sonnet on õigekirja kontrollija, mida kasutavad mitmed &kde; rakendused, "
"näiteks &kate;, &kmail; ja &kword;. See on mitmesuguste vabade õigekirja "
"kontrollimise tööriistade graafiline kasutajaliides."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:669
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To use &sonnet; you need to install a spell checker like "
#| "<application>&GNU; Aspell</application>, <application>Enchant</"
#| "application>, <application>Hspell</application>, <application>ISpell</"
#| "application> or <application>Hunspell</application> and additionally the "
#| "corresponding dictionaries for the languages that you wish to use."
msgid ""
"To use &sonnet; you need to install a spell checker like <application>&GNU; "
"Aspell</application>, <application>Hspell</application> or "
"<application>Hunspell</application> and additionally the corresponding "
"dictionaries for the languages that you wish to use."
msgstr ""
"Sonneti kasutamiseks peab olema paigaldatud mõni õigekirja kontrollimise "
"programm, näiteks <application>&GNU; Aspell</application>, "
"<application>Enchant</application>, <application>Hspell</application>, "
"<application>ISpell</application> või <application>Hunspell</application> "
"ning lisaks vastavad oma keele sõnastikud."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:678
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Check Spelling Window"
msgstr "Õigekirja kontrollimise aken"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:684
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Check spelling window."
msgstr "Õigekirja kontrollimise aken."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:686
#, no-c-format
msgid "Correcting a misspelling."
msgstr "Kirjavea parandamine."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To check spelling, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Spelling...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Õigekirja kontrollimiseks vali menüükäsk <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</"
"guimenu> <guimenuitem>Õigekirja kontroll...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If a word is possibly misspelled in your document, it is displayed in the "
"top line in the dialog. &sonnet; tries to appropriate word(s) for "
"replacement. The best guess is displayed to the right of <guilabel>Replace "
"with</guilabel>. To accept this replacement, click on <guibutton>Replace</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Kui sõna on dokumendis arvatavasti valesti kirjutatud, on see näha dialoogi "
"ülemisel real. Sonnet püüab leida sellele sobiva asenduse. Parimat soovitust "
"näeb kirjest <guilabel>Asendus</guilabel> paremal. Sellega nõustumisel "
"klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Asenda</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&sonnet; also allows you to select a word from the list of suggestions and "
"replace the misspelled word with that selected word. With the help of the "
"<guibutton>Suggest</guibutton> button, you can add more suggestions from the "
"dictionary to the suggestions list."
msgstr ""
"Sonnet võimaldab ka valida sõja soovituste loendist ja asendada valesti "
"kirjutatud sõna valitud sõnaga. Nupu <guibutton>Soovita</guibutton> abil "
"saab soovituste loendisse lisada veel rohkem soovitusi sõnaraamatust."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click on <guibutton>Ignore</guibutton> to keep your original spelling."
msgstr ""
"Algupärase vormi säilitamiseks klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Eira</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Finished</guibutton> to stop spellchecking and "
"<emphasis>keep</emphasis> the changes made."
msgstr ""
"Õigekirja kontrolli peatamiseks ning juba tehtud muudatuste "
"<emphasis>säilitamiseks</emphasis> klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Lõpetatud</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:708
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Cancel</guibutton> to stop spellchecking and "
"<emphasis>cancel</emphasis> the changes already made."
msgstr ""
"Õigekirja kontrolli peatamiseks ning juba tehtud muudatuste "
"<emphasis>tühistamiseks</emphasis> klõpsa nupule  <guibutton>Loobu</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Replace All</guibutton> to automatically replace the "
"misspelled word(s) with the chosen replacement word, if they appear again in "
"your document later."
msgstr ""
"Klõps nupule <guibutton>Asenda kõik</guibutton> asendab valesti kirjutatud "
"sõna valitud sõnaga ka siis, kui see peaks dokumendis uuesti esinema."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:715
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Ignore All</guibutton> to ignore the spelling at that "
"point and all the future occurrences of the word misspelled."
msgstr ""
"Klõps nupule <guibutton>Eira kõiki</guibutton> annab korralduse eirata "
"arvatavalt valesti kirjutatud sõna nii praegu kui ka kõigil järgnevatel "
"esinemiskordadel."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:718
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on <guibutton>Add to Dictionary</guibutton> to add the misspelled word "
"to your personal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Klõps nupule <guibutton>Lisa sõnaraamatusse</guibutton> lisab valesti "
"kirjutatuks arvatud sõna sinu isiklikku sõnaraamatusse."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Personal Dictionary</guilabel> is a distinct dictionary from "
"the system dictionary and the additions made by you will not be seen by "
"others."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Isiklik sõnaraamat</guilabel> on süsteemsest sõnaraamatust lahus "
"olev sõnaraamat, millesse lisatud sõnu ei näe keegi teine."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The drop down box <guilabel>Language</guilabel> at the bottom of this dialog "
"allows you to switch to another dictionary temporarily."
msgstr ""
"Rippmenüü <guilabel>Keel</guilabel> abil dialoogi allosas saab ajutiselt "
"lülituda mõnele muule sõnaraamatule."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:730
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic Spell Checking"
msgstr "Automaatne õigekirja kontroll"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:734
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In many applications, you can automatically check spelling as you type. To "
"enable this feature, select <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Automatic Spell Checking</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Paljudes rakendustes saab lasta õigekirja kontrollida otse kirjutamise ajal. "
"Selle võimaldamiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Õigekirja automaatne kontroll</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Potentially misspelled words will be underlined in red. To select a "
"suggestion, right click on the word, select the <guisubmenu>Spelling</"
"guisubmenu> submenu, and select the suggestion. You may also instruct "
"&sonnet; to ignore this spelling for this document by selecting "
"<guimenuitem>Ignore Word</guimenuitem>, or you may select <guimenuitem>Add "
"to Dictionary</guimenuitem> to save it in your personal dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Sõnad, mis võivad olla valesti kirjutatud, joonitakse punaselt alla. "
"Soovituse saamiseks tee sõnal paremklõps, vali alammenüü "
"<guisubmenu>Õigekirja kontroll</guisubmenu> ja sealt vajalik soovitus. "
"Samuti võib panna Sonneti sellist kirjapilti käesolevas dokumendis eirama, "
"kui valida <guimenuitem>Eira sõna</guimenuitem>, või lisada selle oma "
"isiklikku sõnaraamatusse, kui valida <guimenuitem>Lisa sõnaraamatusse</"
"guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring &sonnet;"
msgstr "Sonneti seadistamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:750
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change your dictionary, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Change Dictionary...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. A small window "
"will appear at the bottom of the current document that will allow you to "
"change your dictionary."
msgstr ""
"Sõnaraamatu muutmiseks vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Tööriistad</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Muuda sõnaraamatut...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Aktiivse "
"dokumendi allosas ilmub väike aken, kus saab sõnaraamatut muuta."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on configuring &sonnet;, see the <ulink url=\"help:/"
"kcontrol/spellchecking\">Spell Checker &systemsettings; module "
"documentation</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Täpsemalt kõneleb Sonneti seadistamisest <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"spellchecking\">Süsteemi seadistuste õigekirja kontrollimise mooduli "
"käsiraamat</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 Participant Salma Sultana for writing "
"much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Suurel määral kirjutas käesoleva osa Google Code-In-2011 osavõtja Salma "
"Sultana."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find and Replace"
msgstr "Otsimine ja asendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:788
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find function of many &kde; applications lets you find specific text in "
"a document, while the Replace function allows you to replace text that is "
"found with different text you provide."
msgstr ""
"Paljudes &kde; rakendustes kasutatav otsimisfunktsioon võimaldab leida "
"dokumendis konkreetset teksti, asendamisfunktsioon aga asendada leitud "
"teksti mingi muu tekstiga."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can find both these functions in the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu of "
"many &kde; applications. For more information on this menu, see <xref "
"linkend=\"menus-edit\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Enamikus &kde; rakendustes leiab mõlemad funktsioonid menüüst "
"<guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu>. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest menüüst <xref "
"linkend=\"menus-edit\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:797
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find Function"
msgstr "Otsimisfunktsioon"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find function searches for text in a document and selects it."
msgstr "Otsimisfunktsioon otsib dokumendis teksti ja leidmisel valib selle."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find Window"
msgstr "Otsimisaken"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:806
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Find window."
msgstr "Otsimisaken."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:807
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Searching for <userinput>software</userinput> in <ulink url=\"http://kde."
#| "org/applications/internet/kmail/\">&kmail;'s composer window</ulink>."
msgid ""
"Searching for <userinput>income</userinput> in <ulink url=\"https://www.kde."
"org/applications/office/sheets/\">&calligrasheets;</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Sõna <userinput>software</userinput> otsimine <ulink url=\"http://kde.org/"
"applications/internet/kmail/\">&kmail;i kirjakoosteaknas</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:813
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To use Find in many applications, go to <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Find...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or press <keycombo action="
"\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Then, in the <guilabel>Text "
"to find:</guilabel> text box, enter the text that you want to find."
msgstr ""
"Otsingu kasutamiseks enamikus rakendustes vali "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Otsi...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> või vajuta <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>F</keycap></keycombo>. Seejärel sisesta kasti <guilabel>Otsitav "
"tekst</guilabel> see tekst, mida soovid leida."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If <guilabel>Regular expression</guilabel> is checked you will be able to "
"search using regular expressions. Click on <guibutton>Edit</guibutton> to "
"select from and enter commonly used regular expression characters, like "
"<guilabel>White Space</guilabel> or <guilabel>Start of Line</guilabel>. If "
"&kate; is installed, you can find <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-"
"expressions.html\">more information on writing regular expressions in its "
"documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kui märkida kastike <guilabel>Regulaaravaldis</guilabel>, saab otsingul "
"kasutada regulaaravaldisi. Klõpsa <guibutton>Muuda</guibutton>, et valida "
"või sisestada levinumaid regulaaravaldiste märke, näiteks "
"<guilabel>tühimärk</guilabel> või <guilabel>rea algus</guilabel>. Kui "
"paigaldatud on &kate;, leiab <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions."
"html\">rohkem teavet regulaaravaldise kirjutamise kohta selle käsiraamatust</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:828
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can limit the found results by configuring these options:"
msgstr "Otsingutulemusi saab piirata järgmiste valikutega:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid "Case sensitive"
msgstr "Tõstutundlik"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Capital and lowercase characters are considered different. For example, if "
"you search for <quote>This</quote>, results that contain <quote>this</quote> "
"will not be returned."
msgstr ""
"Sel juhul peetakse suur- ja väiketähti erinevaks. Kui näiteks otsida "
"<quote>See</quote>, siis ei näidata tulemusi, milles leidub <quote>see</"
"quote>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:839
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whole words only"
msgstr "Ainult terved sõnad"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:840
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, when the application searches for text, it will return results "
"even in the middle of other text. For instance, if you search for <quote>is</"
"quote> it will stop on every word that contains that, like "
"<quote>th<emphasis>is</emphasis></quote> or <quote>h<emphasis>is</"
"emphasis>tory</quote>. If you check this option, the application will only "
"return results when the search text is a word by itself, that is, surrounded "
"by whitespace."
msgstr ""
"Teksti otsimisel tagastatakse vaikimisi tulemused ka siis, kui otsitav asub "
"keset muud teksti. Kui näiteks otsida <quote>see</quote>, siis leitakse kõik "
"seda sisaldavad sõnad, näiteks <quote>be<emphasis>see</emphasis></quote> või "
"<quote>re<emphasis>see</emphasis>da</quote>. Selle valiku märkimisel "
"tagastab rakendus tulemused ainult siis, kui otsingutekst esineb tervikliku "
"sõnana, see tähendab seda ümbritsevad tühimärgid."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:850
#, no-c-format
msgid "From cursor"
msgstr "Kursorist alates"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search will start from the location of the cursor and stop at the end of "
"the text."
msgstr "Otsing algab kursori asukohast ja lõpeb teksti lõpus."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find backwards"
msgstr "Otsimine tagasisuunas"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:857
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the application searches for the text starting at the beginning "
"of the document, and move through it to the end. If you check this option, "
"it will instead start at the end and work its way to the beginning."
msgstr ""
"Vaikimisi hakatakse teksti otsima dokumendi algusest ja liigutakse selle "
"lõppu. Selle valiku märkimisel alustatakse aga lõpust ja lõpetatakse alguses."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selected text"
msgstr "Valitud tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:865
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select this option to search only in the text that is currently selected, "
"not the entire document. It is disabled when no text is selected."
msgstr ""
"Selle märkimisel otsitakse otsingusõna ainult valitud tekstist, mitte kogu "
"dokumendist. Seda ei saa märkida, kui teksti pole valitud."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:875
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Applications which use the &kde; text editor component show a search bar "
#| "instead of the Find window. See <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-"
#| "find-replace.html#finding-text\">&katepart; documentation</ulink> for "
#| "additional information on the search bar."
msgid ""
"Many applications show a search bar instead of the Find window. See <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace.html#finding-text\">&katepart; "
"documentation</ulink> for additional information on the search bar."
msgstr ""
"Rakendustes, mis kasutavad &kde; tekstiredaktori komponenti, näeb "
"otsimisakna asemel otsimisriba. Täpsemat teavet otsimisriba kohta annab "
"<ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace.html#finding-text"
"\">&katepart;i dokumentatsioon</ulink>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The search bar in &kate;.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Otsimisriba &kate;s.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:883
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The search bar in &kate;.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Otsimisriba &kate;s.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:884
#, no-c-format
msgid "Searching for <userinput>software</userinput> in &kate;'s search bar."
msgstr "<userinput>software</userinput> otsimine &kate; otsinguribal."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Find function only selects the first match that it finds. You can "
"continue searching by selecting <menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Find Next</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or by pressing "
"<keycap>F3</keycap>."
msgstr ""
"Otsimisfunktsioon valib ainult esimese leitud vaste. Otsingut saab jätkata, "
"kui valida <menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu><guimenuitem>Otsi "
"järgmine</guimenuitem></menuchoice> või vajutada <keycap>F3</keycap>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example of a Search"
msgstr "Otsimise näide"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:897
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example of a search."
msgstr "Otsimise näide."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:898
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "&kmail; displays a match for <userinput>software</userinput>."
msgid "&kate; displays a match for <userinput>KDE</userinput>."
msgstr "&kmail; näitab otsingu <userinput>software</userinput> tulemust."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:906
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace Function"
msgstr "Asendamisfunktsioon"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Replace function searches for text in a document and replaces it with "
"other text. You can find it in many application at "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Edit</guimenu><guisubmenu>Replace...</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> or by pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Asendamisfunktsioon otsib dokumendis teksti ja asendab selle mingi muu "
"tekstiga. Enamikus rakendustes saab seda funktsiooni kasutada menüükäsuga "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Redigeerimine</guimenu><guisubmenu>Asenda...</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> või klahvikombinatsiooniga <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:915
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace Window"
msgstr "Asendamisaken"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:918
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Replace window."
msgstr "Asendamisaken."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:919
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Replacing <userinput>food</userinput> with <userinput>drink</userinput> "
#| "in &kmail;"
msgid ""
"Replacing <userinput>income</userinput> with <userinput>expense</userinput> "
"in &calligrasheets;"
msgstr ""
"Sõna <userinput>toit</userinput> asendamine sõnaga <userinput>jook</"
"userinput> &kmail;is"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:924
#, no-c-format
msgid "The window of the Replace function is separated into 3 sections:"
msgstr "Asendamisaken jaguneb kolmeks osaks:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:928
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Otsing"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you may enter the text you wish to search for. See <xref linkend=\"find-"
"find\"/> for more information on the options provided here."
msgstr ""
"Siin saab sisestada teksti, mida tahad leida. Täpsemalt kõneleb siinsetest "
"valikutest <xref linkend=\"find-find\"/>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:935
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Asendamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:937
#, no-c-format
msgid "Here you may enter the text you wish to replace the found text with."
msgstr "Siin saab sisestada teksti, millega tahad asendada leitud teksti."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:939
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reuse the found text in the replacement text by selecting the "
"<guilabel>Use placeholders</guilabel> checkbox. Placeholders, sometimes "
"known as backreferences, are a special character sequence that will be "
"replaced with all or part of the found text. For instance, <quote>\\0</"
"quote> represents the entire found string."
msgstr ""
"Soovi korral saab leitud teksti asendustekstis ära kasutada, kui märkida "
"kastike <guilabel>Kohatäitjate kasutamine</guilabel>. Kohatäitjad on "
"erilised märgijadad, mis asendatakse kogu või osalise leitud tekstiga. "
"Näiteks <quote>\\0</quote> tähendab kogu leitud stringi."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may insert placeholders into the text box by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Insert Placeholder</guibutton> button, then selecting an option "
"from the menu like <guimenuitem>Complete Match</guimenuitem>. For example, "
"if you are searching for <quote>message</quote>, and you want to replace it "
"with <guilabel>messages</guilabel> insert the <guimenuitem>Complete Match</"
"guimenuitem> placeholder and add an <quote>s</quote>. The replace field will "
"then contain <quote>\\0s</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Kohatäitjaid saab tekstikasti lisada klõpsuga nupule <guibutton>Lisa "
"kohatäitja</guibutton> ja seejärel menüüst vajalikku valikut valides, "
"näiteks <guimenuitem>Täielik sobivus</guimenuitem>. Kui näiteks otsid sõna "
"<quote>sõnum</quote> ja soovid selle asendada sõnaga <guilabel>sõnumid</"
"guilabel>, siis lisa <guimenuitem>täieliku sobivuse</guimenuitem> kohatäitja "
"ja sellele <quote>id</quote>. Sel juhul seisab asendamisväljal nüüd <quote>"
"\\0id</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If &kate; is installed, you can learn more about placeholders in the <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\">Regular Expressions appendix "
"of its documentation</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Kui paigaldatud on &kate;, saab rohkem teavet kohatäitjate kohta <ulink url="
"\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\">selle käsiraamatu "
"regulaaravaldusi käsitlevast lisast</ulink>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Options</guilabel>"
msgstr "<guilabel>Valikud</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:960
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This contains all the same options that the <link linkend=\"find-find"
"\">Find</link> function does, with one addition:"
msgstr ""
"Siit leiab samad valikud nagu <link linkend=\"find-find"
"\">otsimisfunktsiooni</link> alt ja veel ühe:"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:962
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Prompt on replace</guilabel> option is checked a window "
"will appear on every found word, allowing you to confirm whether you would "
"like to replace the found text."
msgstr ""
"Kui märgitud on <guilabel>Asendamisel küsitakse</guilabel>, ilmub iga leitud "
"sõna korral aken, kus saab kinnitada, et soovid leitud teksti asendada, või "
"siis sellest loobuda."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:972
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Applications which use the &kde; text editor component show a search and "
#| "replace bar instead of the Replace window. See <ulink url=\"help:/kwrite/"
#| "edit.html#replace\">&kwrite; documentation</ulink> for additional "
#| "information on the search and replace bar."
msgid ""
"Many Applications show a search and replace bar instead of the Replace "
"window. See <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/kate-part-find-replace."
"html#replacing-text\">&katepart; documentation</ulink> for additional "
"information on the search and replace bar."
msgstr ""
"Rakendustes, mis kasutavad &kde; tekstiredaktori komponenti, näeb "
"asendamisakna asemel otsimis- ja asendamisriba. Täpsemat teavet otsimis- ja "
"asendamisriba kohta annab <ulink url=\"help:/kwrite/edit.html#replace"
"\">&kwrite;'i käsiraamat</ulink>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:978
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The search and replace bar.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Otsimis- ja asendamisriba.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:981
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The search and replace bar.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Otsimis- ja asendamisriba.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:982
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replacing <userinput>kmail</userinput> with <userinput>kate</userinput> in "
"&kate;'s search and replace bar"
msgstr ""
"Sõna <userinput>kmail</userinput> asendamine sõnaga <userinput>kate</"
"userinput> &kate; otsimis- ja asendamisribal."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Thanks to an anonymous Google Code-In 2011 participant for writing much of "
"this section."
msgstr ""
"Tänu suure osa materjali kirjutamise eest kuulub ühele Google'i Code-In 2011 "
"anonüümsele osavõtjale."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1005
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing Fonts"
msgstr "Fontide valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1007
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The font selector appears in many different &kde; applications. It lets you "
"select the font face, font style, and font size of the text that appears in "
"your application."
msgstr ""
"Fondivalija on kasutusel paljudes &kde; rakendustes. See võimaldab valida "
"rakenduses nähtava teksti fondi tüübi, stiili ja suuruse."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:1012
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Font Selector"
msgstr "Fondivalija"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid "The font selector."
msgstr "Fondivalija."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1016
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting a font in <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Fondi valimine <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">Süsteemi seadistustes</"
"ulink>"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font"
msgstr "Font"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1025
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the leftmost selection box, and lets you choose the font face from a "
"list of fonts on your system."
msgstr ""
"See on vasakpoolseim valikukast, kus saab süsteemi paigaldatud fontide seast "
"valida vajaliku."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1030
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font style"
msgstr "Fondi stiil"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1032
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the center selection box, and lets you choose the font style from "
"the following choices:"
msgstr ""
"See on keskmine valikukast, kus saab valida fondistiili järgmiste võimaluste "
"seast:"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Italic</guilabel> - this displays text in a cursive, or slanted "
"fashion, and is commonly used for citations or to emphasize text."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Kaldkiri</guilabel> - sel juhul näidatakse teksti kursiivis ehk "
"kaldu, mis on levinud näiteks tsitaatide või tekstirõhutuste korral."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1040
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Regular</guilabel> - the default. Text is displayed without any "
"special appearance."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Tavaline</guilabel> - vaikevälimus. Teksti näidatakse ilma mingite "
"erivõteteta."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1043
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bold Italic</guilabel> - a combination of both <guilabel>Bold</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Italic</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Rasvane kaldkiri</guilabel> - ühendab nii <guilabel>rasvase</"
"guilabel> kui ka <guilabel>kaldkirja</guilabel>"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Bold</guilabel> - this displays text in a darker, thicker fashion, "
"and is commonly used for titles of documents or to emphasize text."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Rasvane</guilabel> - teksti näidatakse paksema ja tumedamana, mida "
"kasutatakse sageli dokumendi pealkirjades või teksti rõhutamiseks."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: tasks.docbook:1055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size"
msgstr "Suurus"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1056
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This is the rightmost selection box, and lets you select the size of your "
#| "text. Font size is measured in <emphasis>points</emphasis>, a standard "
#| "unit of measure in typography. For more information on this, see <ulink "
#| "url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_(typography)\">the <quote>Point "
#| "(typography)</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgid ""
"This is the rightmost selection box, and lets you select the size of your "
"text. Font size is measured in <emphasis>points</emphasis>, a standard unit "
"of measure in typography. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_(typography)\">the <quote>Point "
"(typography)</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"See on parempoolseim valikukast, kus saab valida teksti suuruse. Fondi "
"suurust mõõdetakse <emphasis>punktides</emphasis>, mis on tüpograafias "
"levinud mõõtühik. Täpsemalt kõneleb selles artikkel <ulink url=\"http://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Point_(typography)\"><quote>Point (typography)</quote> "
"Wikipedias</ulink>."

#. Tag: term
#: tasks.docbook:1064
#, no-c-format
msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Eelvaatlus"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1065
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The bottom of the font selector displays a preview of text using the font "
"settings that are currently selected. You may change this text if you wish."
msgstr ""
"Fondivalija allosas näeb teksti eelvaatlust vastavalt ülal paiknevates "
"valikukastides langetatud valikutele. Soovi korral võib näidatavat teksti "
"muuta."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1081
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing Colors"
msgstr "Värvide valimine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1083
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color chooser appears in many &kde; applications, whenever you need to "
"select a color. It lets you pick from a <guilabel>Basic colors</guilabel> "
"consisting of many predefined colors or mix your own when you want a "
"specific color."
msgstr ""
"Värvivalijat kohtab paljudes &kde; rakendustes, kus on vähegi vajalik värvi "
"valida. See võimaldab valida värvi <guilabel>põhivärvide</guilabel> seast, "
"mis sisaldavad juba paljusid valmisvärve, või ka segada kokku just endale "
"meeldiva värvi."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: tasks.docbook:1088
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Color Selector"
msgstr "Värvivalija"

#. Tag: phrase
#: tasks.docbook:1091
#, no-c-format
msgid "The color selector."
msgstr "Värvivalija."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selecting a color in <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">&systemsettings;</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Värvi valimine <ulink url=\"help:/systemsettings\">Süsteemi seadistustes</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1098
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Basic Colors"
msgstr "Põhivärvide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The basic colors group is a set of predefined colors. You can find it on the "
"top side of the color chooser window."
msgstr ""
"Põhivärvid koondavad hulka valmisvärve. Need leiab värvi valimise akna "
"ülaosas."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select a color from the basic colors, simply click on it. The color will "
"be displayed at the right of the palette, along with its &HTML; hexadecimal "
"code"
msgstr ""
"Värvi valimiseks põhivärvide seast lihtsalt klõpsa sellel. Värvi näeb "
"paletist paremal koos selle &HTML; kuueteistkümnendkoodiga."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Mixing Colors"
msgstr "Värvide segamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The color chooser also lets you mix your own colors. There are several ways "
"to do this:"
msgstr ""
"Värvivalija laseb kokku segada ka täpselt endale meeldiva värvi. Seda saab "
"teha mitmel viisil:"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Grid"
msgstr "Ruudustiku abil"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The right side of the color chooser contains a large box, and a thinner box "
"immediately to its right. You can use the left box to select the Hue and "
"Saturation of the desired color based on the visual guide provided in the "
"box. The right bar adjusts the Value. Adjust these to select the desired "
"color, which is displayed in the middle of the window."
msgstr ""
"Värvivalija paremal küljel on suur kast ja sellest otse paremal veel üks "
"peenike kast. Vasakpoolses kastis saab valida kastis olevat visuaalset "
"eeskuju jälgides soovitud värvi tooni ja küllastuse. Parempoolne kitsas kast "
"laseb täpsustada värvi väärtust. Muuda neid, kuni saad vajaliku värvi, mis "
"on näha akna keskmises osas."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information on Hue, Saturation, and Value, see <xref linkend="
"\"colors-mixing-hsv\"/>"
msgstr ""
"Täpsemat teavet tooni, küllastuse ja väärtuse kohta annab <xref linkend="
"\"colors-mixing-hsv\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Screen Colors"
msgstr "Ekraanivärvide kasutamine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The eyedropper tool allows you to select a color from your screen. To use "
"it, select the <guibutton>Pick Screen Color</guibutton> button below the "
"basic colors, and then click anywhere on your screen to select that color."
msgstr ""
"Pipett võimaldab valida värvi otse ekraanilt. Selleks vali "
"<guibutton>pipeti</guibutton> nupp otse põhivärvidest allpool ja klõpsa "
"ekraanil kohas, mille värvi tahad valida."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hue/Saturation/Value"
msgstr "Toon, küllastus, väärtus"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower-right corner of the screen allows you to manually enter the "
"coordinates of the desired color in the Hue/Saturation/Value (<acronym>HSV</"
"acronym>) color space. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HSL_and_HSV\">the <quote>HSL and HSV</quote> "
"article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Ekraani alumises parempoolses osas saab käsitsi sisestada soovitud värvi "
"koordinaadid tooni, küllastuse ja väärtuse (<acronym>HSV</acronym>) "
"värviruumis. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/"
"wiki/HSL_and_HSV\">artikkel <quote>HSL and HSV</quote> Wikipedias</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1147 tasks.docbook:1161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These values are also updated when selecting a color by other methods, so "
"they always accurately represent the currently selected color."
msgstr ""
"Neid väärtusi uuendatakse ka siis, kui valid värvi mõnel muul viisil, nii et "
"alati näitavad nad parajasti valitud värvi täpseid väärtusi"

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Red/Green/Blue"
msgstr "Punane, roheline ja sinine"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1155
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower-right corner of the screen also allows you to manually enter the "
"coordinates of the desired color in the Red/Green/Blue (<acronym>RGB</"
"acronym>) color model. For more information on this, see <ulink url="
"\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/RGB_color_model\">the <quote>RGB color "
"model</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Samuti saab ekraani alumises parempoolses osas käsitsi sisestada soovitud "
"värvi koordinaadid punase, rohelise ja sinise (<acronym>RGB</acronym>) "
"värvimudelis. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia."
"org/wiki/RGB_color_model\">artikkel <quote>RGB color model</quote> "
"Wikipedias</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1167
#, no-c-format
msgid "&HTML; Hexadecimal Code"
msgstr "&HTML; kuueteistkümnendkood"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1169
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You may enter the &HTML; hexadecimal code representing the color in the "
#| "lower-right corner of the screen. For more information on this, see "
#| "<ulink url=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_colors\">the <quote>Web "
#| "colors</quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgid ""
"You may enter the &HTML; hexadecimal code representing the color in the "
"lower-right corner of the screen. For more information on this, see <ulink "
"url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_colors\">the <quote>Web colors</"
"quote> article on Wikipedia</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Soovi korral võib ekraani alumisse parempoolsesse ossa sisestada värvi "
"tähistava &HTML; kuueteistkümnendkoodi. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest <ulink url="
"\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Web_colors\">artikkel <quote>Web colors</"
"quote> Wikipedias</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This value is also updated when selecting a color by other methods, so it "
"always accurately represents the currently selected color."
msgstr ""
"Ka seda väärtust uuendatakse, kui valid värvi mõnel muul viisil, nii et "
"seegi näitab alati parajasti valitud värvi täpset väärtust."

#. Tag: title
#: tasks.docbook:1181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom Colors"
msgstr "Kohandatud värvid"

#. Tag: para
#: tasks.docbook:1183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After selecting a color, you may add it to the Custom Colors group so you "
"can use it later. To do so, click the <guibutton>Add to Custom Colors</"
"guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Värvi valimise järel võib selle lisada kohandatud värvide rühma, et seda "
"saaks ka hiljem kasutada. Selleks klõpsa nupule <guibutton>Lisa kohandatud "
"värvidesse</guibutton>."

#~ msgid "Using Palettes"
#~ msgstr "Palettide kasutamine"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "To switch between them, use the drop down box above the color palette. "
#~ "Most palettes will display a grid consisting of the colors, except for "
#~ "the <guilabel>Named Colors</guilabel>, which lets you select from a list "
#~ "of names. Other special palettes include <guilabel>* Recent Colors *</"
#~ "guilabel>, which will display colors that you have recently selected, and "
#~ "<guilabel>* Custom Colors *</guilabel>, which will display custom colors "
#~ "that you have saved. For more information on setting custom colors, see "
#~ "<xref linkend=\"colors-custom\"/>"
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Nende vahel lülitamiseks kasuta värvipaleti kohal asuvat rippmenüüd. "
#~ "Enamik palette näitab värvidega ruudustikku, välja arvatud "
#~ "<guilabel>Nimega värvid</guilabel>, mis lubab valida värvi nime järgi. "
#~ "Eripaletid on samuti <guilabel>* Viimati kasutatud värvid *</guilabel>, "
#~ "mis sisaldab viimati valitud värve, ja <guilabel>* Kohandatud värvid *</"
#~ "guilabel>, mis näitab kohandatud värve, mille oled salvestanud. Täpsemalt "
#~ "kõneleb kohandatud värvidega seonduvast <xref linkend=\"colors-custom\"/>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "After selecting a color, you may save it to the Custom Colors palette so "
#~ "you can find it later. To do so, click the <guibutton>Add to Custom "
#~ "Colors</guibutton> button. You can then find it by selecting the "
#~ "<guilabel>* Custom Colors *</guilabel> palette from the drop down box in "
#~ "the upper-right corner of the screen. For more information on using "
#~ "palettes, see <xref linkend=\"colors-palette\"/>."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Pärast värvi valimist võib selle salvestada kohandatud värvide paletti, "
#~ "et see vajaduse korral hiljem taas üles leida. Selleks klõpsa nupule "
#~ "<guibutton>Lisa kohandatud värvidesse</guibutton>. Hiljem leiab värvi, "
#~ "kui valida ekraani ülemises parempoolses osas asuvast rippmenüüst "
#~ "<guilabel>* Kohandatud värvid *</guilabel>. Palettide kasutamisest "
#~ "kõneleb täpsemalt <xref linkend=\"colors-palette\"/>."

#~ msgid "The search bar &kate;."
#~ msgstr "&kate; otsinguriba."

#~ msgid "The search bar in kate;."
#~ msgstr "&kate; otsinguriba."
